@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uneiyv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v1 + 0.59 / v2 + 0.11)))
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.71)) / wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.48)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.26) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.11)) * wp.abs((v1 + 0.88 * v2 + 0.18)))
    v1 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.97 / v1 + 0.16)) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.04) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.72)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v1) - v2)
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.64 / v1 + 0.86)) * wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.86)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
